Titolo: Man vs. Wild (video game)

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: Man vs. Wild  is a video game inspired by the Man vs. Wild survival television series. In it, the player takes on the role of host Bear Grylls to survive the hardships of various environments. It was developed by American companies Floor 84 Studio and Scientifically Proven.
The game targeted all major seventh-generation platforms, but the handheld versions were ultimately cancelled.



Genere: Action 

Valutazione: N/A
